medical_history.chief_complaint: Fussiness and potential bone injury following accidental drop.
medical_history.history_of_present_illness: Symptoms became apparent after the infant was accidentally dropped onto a plush carpet from a distance of two feet. The infant was immediately fussy after the incident.
medical_history.family_history: The mother is unaware of anyone in her family having a disease.
medical_history.social_history: The mother did not have any prenatal care due to lack of insurance. The mother has a robust family support system, no other children, and her husband recently began working as a firefighter who remains on-call throughout the week.
